      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's honestly been such a champ! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for all my daily trips. It\u2019s got that 'perfectly broken-in' feel\u2014runs smooth, looks great, and is totally ready for its next big adventure with you. If you're looking for a reliable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one! Come give it a test drive and see for yourself!",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
