      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54B32 inline-six, delivering power through six individual throttle bodies and a precise 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis is well-sorted with a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed suspension bushings to maintain structural rigidity. Recent preventative maintenance includes a VANOS overhaul and shim-and-bucket valve adjustment, ensuring the valvetrain meets factory specifications. With its factory limited-slip differential and communicative hydraulic steering, this example delivers a pure analog driving experience. It shows minor cosmetic wear consistent with its age, but the powertrain and drivetrain remain robust and high-performing.",
